oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Learn about life on Mt. LeConte at library presentation May 21
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: The Daily Times
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: A newspaper article promoting a presentation by Nathan Kirkham called 'Life on Mount LeConte: Four Years as an Ambassador at the Top of Tennessee' as part of the Southern Appalachian Study Series at the Blount County Public Library.
